Hellu infra, I have a question.

Why is it that some projects in perf.rust-lang.org/compare.html don't have any incr-patched test? Were those tests not interesting enough, were they too heavy to run, what was it?
I ask because my thesis (which will be in mir-opts) will use these tests :P and I have to describe the statistics of them in detail now. Any insight on this is appreciated :sunflower:
